Problem Statement -->

Objective: Swing
Modify the solution of 12.1 so such the game can be played via mouse. In other words add a graphical user interface to 12.1. The graphical interface must allow at least the following:
1.) Setting up the fleet
2.) Join with the server
3.) Detach from the server
4.) Allow to enter the players name
5.) Update the ocean after each players move on both clients
6.) Indicate when a client can make a move
7.) Indicate if a player won or lost.
8.) It must be resizable (a minimum size must exist)
9.) You might add more functionality
